# NORT Phase Two — Full Hackathon Architecture Plan

> **Hackathon**: Base Batches | **Network**: Base (testnet → mainnet)
> **AI Agent Intern Scope**: `services/agent/` + `services/backend/api/advice.py`

---

## ⚠️ Critical Architecture Fact: Base vs Polymarket

> [!IMPORTANT]
> Polymarket runs on **Polygon**, not Base. This is a fundamental constraint.
> Your options:
> - **Bridge approach**: User holds USDC on Base → bridge to Polygon to execute on real Polymarket
> - **Parallel prediction market on Base**: Use Polymarket data for prices/markets, but settle trades through a custom Base smart contract (simulated Polymarket on-chain)
> - **Recommended for hackathon**: Use Base for wallet + payments + settlement receipt; route actual Polymarket trades via their CLOB API on Polygon. The "on Base" story is the wallet and payment layer.

---

