## Hackathon Demo Script (Base Batches)

```
1. User loads wallet via MPesa → USDC appears in Telegram wallet
2. /advice market-001 → shows structured AI advice with confidence 0.82
3. User asks follow-up "What if odds drop to 60%?" → agent responds in context
4. /enable_autotrade → user sets auto-trade, $30 limit, confidence 0.75
5. /advice triggers → AutoTradeEngine fires → real USDC trade on Polymarket
6. Dashboard shows on-chain tx hash as proof
7. /premium_advice → locked, user pays $0.10 USDC via x402 → unlocks
8. /language sw → repeat in Kiswahili
```

This tells a complete Base-native story: **wallet on Base → pay via x402 on Base → agent executes real trade → receipt on-chain**.
